I"þ<h2 id="learning-objectives">Learning Objectives</h2>

<p>The learning goals for this module are:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Discuss the basics of Time Series Analysis (TSA): background, motivation, definition, components, etc; <br /></li>
  <li>Go over R and RStudio basics such as how to install packages, importing and exporting data, making plots; <br /></li>
  <li>Introduce best practices on coding: creating well commented scripts, loading packages, adding header. <br /></li>
</ul>

