<h2 id="topics-for-discussionreflection">Topics for Discussion/Reflection</h2>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>How much the advent and success of Smart Grids depend on the full roll out of Smart Meters? <br /></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Knowing how the internet developed and changes our daily lives, can we draw a parallel with Smart Grids and predict their evolution in the future? <br /></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>How to educate consumers on how to use smart grid? <br /></p>
  </li>
</ul>

